snippet.title: Down To One - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Up to 42 players start. 1 will survive. 
Start out with nothing in a harsh, desert environment, and use whatever supplies you can find to outsmart & outlast each other. 

Down To One on Steam http://store.steampowered.com//app/334040?beta=0

Down To One on Twitter https://twitter.com/DownToOneGame
